# Unpacked Extension Debug Playbook

- For “rule exists but not applied” bugs, verify in service worker console:
  - `chrome.declarativeNetRequest.getDynamicRules()`
  - inspect `condition.regexFilter` and `removeParams`
- If rule schema/generation changed, remind to delete and re-add existing user rules so stored data reflects new shape.
- Treat this project as local-only unless code shows explicit network dependency.
- Distinguish parser truth (`URLSearchParams`) from raw URL string truth (regex on request URL).
- When uncertain, create a minimal reproduction URL and test candidate regex patterns against it.
